{"an4.145:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 4.145 ","an4.145:0.2":"15. Abhavagga ","an4.145:0.3":"Pajjotasutta ","an4.145:1.1":"“Cattarome, bhikkhave, pajjota. ","an4.145:1.2":"Katame cattaro? ","an4.145:1.3":"Candapajjoto, suriyapajjoto, aggipajjoto, pannapajjoto—","an4.145:1.4":"Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattaro pajjota. ","an4.145:1.5":"Etadaggam, bhikkhave, imesam catunnam pajjotanam yadidam pannapajjoto”ti. ","an4.145:1.6":"Pancamam. "}